| Make_TS.oby - PipeDream-Manuals

IfThere $.Temp Then Else %CDir $.Temp

Set pd$Disc $.Temp.PDManuals_20140207
| Remember to update RiscPkg.Control too

%CDir <pd$Disc>

X %Wipe <pd$Disc>.* ~cfr~v

%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps
%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals
%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream

%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.tutorial
%Copy <Obey$Dir>.tutorial.*        <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.tutorial.* ~rf~cln~v
%SetType                           <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.tutorial.index/html &FAF

%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.tutorial.images
%Copy <Obey$Dir>.tutorial.images.* <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.tutorial.images.* ~rf~cln~v

%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.refguide
%Copy <Obey$Dir>.refguide.*        <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.refguide.* ~rf~cln~v
%SetType                           <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.refguide.index/html &FAF

%CDir <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.refguide.images
%Copy <Obey$Dir>.refguide.images.* <pd$Disc>.Apps.Manuals.PipeDream.refguide.images.* ~rf~cln~v

%CDir                              <pd$Disc>.RiscPkg
%Copy <Obey$Dir>.RiscPkg.Control   <pd$Disc>.RiscPkg.* ~rf~cln~v
%Copy <Obey$Dir>.RiscPkg.Copyright <pd$Disc>.RiscPkg.* ~rf~cln~v

Filer_OpenDir <pd$Disc>
